OL,3,CPolice issue update on investigation
OL,4,Cinto funeral directors
OL,6,FIn an update on Saturday, Assistant
OL,7,FChief Constable Thom McLoughlin said:
OL,8,F"We received a report on Wednesday, 6
OL,9,FMarch, expressing concern about the
OL,10,Fstorage and management processes
OL,11,Frelating to care of the deceased in
OL,12,Fthese locations.
OL,14,F"Since the initial report was made on
OL,15,FWednesday, 6 March, teams of highly
OL,16,Fskilled detectives and specially
OL,17,Ftrained staff from Humberside Police
OL,18,Fhave been working closely with partner
OL,19,Fagencies, including Hull City Council,
OL,20,FEast Riding of Yorkshire Council and
OL,21,FHis Majesty's Coroner.
