OL,3,CPolice issue update on investigation
OL,4,Cinto funeral directors
OL,6,F"Together we have been conducting
OL,7,Fextensive enquiries to fully
OL,8,Funderstand the circumstances and
OL,9,Fconcerns expressed in the report made
OL,10,Fto us.
OL,12,F"As part of this, we are now in the
OL,13,Fprocess of moving a number of deceased
OL,14,Ffrom the premises on Hessle Road in
OL,15,FHull to the local authority mortuary
OL,16,Fin Hull."
OL,18,FPolice said specially trained family
OL,19,Fliaison officers have spoken to
OL,20,Ffamilies involved and will continue to
OL,21,Fdo so.
