OL,4,Cinto funeral directors
OL,6,FA phone line has been set up for those
OL,7,Fwith concerns about loved ones as a
OL,8,Fresult of the investigation - it is
OL,9,F0800 051 4674 or 0207 126 7619 if you
OL,10,Fare calling from abroad.
OL,12,FAcc McLoughlin said: "We have already
OL,13,Freceived a number of calls from
OL,14,Fconcerned members of the public and I
OL,15,Fwant to offer my personal reassurance
OL,16,Fthat we are working as hard as
OL,17,Fpossible to make direct contact with
OL,18,Feach and every family that may have
OL,19,Fbeen affected by the concerns reported.
