OL,3,CPolice issue update on investigation
OL,4,Cinto funeral directors
OL,6,F"I do want to please ask the public to
OL,7,Fremain respectful and refrain from
OL,8,Fspeculation. At the core of this
OL,9,Finvestigation will be heartbroken and
OL,10,Fdevastated families and we ask for the
OL,11,Futmost respect for bereaved families
OL,12,Fwithin our community."
OL,14,FPolice said both Hull City Council and
OL,15,FEast Riding of Yorkshire Council were
OL,16,Fassisting the force in supporting
OL,17,Ffamilies.
